---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { getContent } from '../lib/content';
const content = await getContent();
---
<Base title="Safety & Conduct">
<div class="conduct-page">

  <section class="cond-hero">
    <div class="cond-tag">Safety & Conduct</div>
    <h1 class="cond-h1" set:html={content.conduct_title}></h1>
    <p class="cond-sub">{content.conduct_subtitle}</p>
  </section>

  <!-- EVERYONE'S WELCOME -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">Everyone's welcome here</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">All ages, all backgrounds, all brain types. Quiet, loud, awkward, outgoing — doesn't matter. A few things we want people to know:</p>
    <div class="cond-grid">
      <div class="cond-card">
        <strong>🧠 All brains welcome</strong>
        <p>Neurodivergent, autistic, ADHD, social anxiety — you're good here. Be quiet, leave early, skip small talk, ask questions. There's no "right way" to hang out.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cond-card">
        <strong>👋 Show up as you are</strong>
        <p>Half the people here describe themselves as awkward. That's kind of the point. Nobody's performing. Nobody's keeping score on how social you are.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cond-card">
        <strong>💜 Not a dating app</strong>
        <p>People are here to make friends. If something happens naturally, cool — but don't come here to hit on people. Read the room.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cond-card">
        <strong>🚪 Leave whenever</strong>
        <p>Hit your limit? Social battery dead? Just go. You don't owe anyone an explanation. No one will be weird about it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SAFETY -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">How we keep things safe</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">A few things are built into how this works:</p>
    <div class="cond-list-simple">
      <div>📍 <strong>Locations hidden</strong> until you RSVP</div>
      <div>📞 <strong>Host contact</strong> shared only with attendees</div>
      <div>👤 <strong>Every event has a named host</strong> — someone's always accountable</div>
      <div>✋ <strong>Events are moderated</strong> before going live</div>
      <div>👥 <strong>Small groups</strong> — 6 to 12 people max</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOR WOMEN -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">For women</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">We know meetups can feel different if you're a woman. Here's what we want you to know:</p>
    <div class="cond-callout women">
      <div class="cond-check-list">
        <div><span class="cond-ck">✓</span> If someone makes you uncomfortable, tell the host or reach out to us. You don't need proof — your word is enough.</div>
        <div><span class="cond-ck">✓</span> Your info stays private. Other members only see your first name and neighborhood.</div>
        <div><span class="cond-ck">✓</span> Bring a friend your first time if you want. RSVP for both.</div>
        <div><span class="cond-ck">✓</span> Most events are in public places. If someone hosts at their home, the event will say so upfront.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE LINE -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">Where's the line?</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">We're pretty relaxed. But if someone says you made them uncomfortable, we're going to listen. These get you removed immediately:</p>
    <div class="cond-callout red">
      <div class="cond-check-list">
        <div><span class="cond-x">✕</span> Harassment or making someone feel unsafe</div>
        <div><span class="cond-x">✕</span> Threatening or intimidating anyone</div>
        <div><span class="cond-x">✕</span> Following someone after an event</div>
        <div><span class="cond-x">✕</span> Sharing someone's location or private info</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="cond-p" style="margin-top:14px">Anything else — being rude, too drunk, trying to sell people something — someone will just talk to you about it.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- HOSTING + REPORTING -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">Hosting & reporting</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">Anyone can host. You pick the spot, set the vibe, and help people find you. You're not a bouncer — everyone who shows up is responsible for themselves.</p>
    <p class="cond-p">If something happens at an event, talk to the host, hop in the Discord, or email Seth. We'll keep it between us.</p>
    <div class="cond-btns">
      <a href="https://discord.gg/S8SFNkdSgK" class="cond-btn discord" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discord</a>
      <a href="mailto:stharpe98@gmail.com" class="cond-btn email">Email Seth</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSER -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <div class="cond-callout blue">
      <p><strong>Real talk:</strong> Being awkward? Normal. Saying something dumb? Happens. Running late because I-25 is a parking lot? Every single time. This page isn't about being perfect — it's so everyone can relax and have fun. If you read this far, you're exactly the kind of person we want around.</p>
      <a href="/events" class="cond-cta">See what's coming up →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style is:inline>
  .conduct-page { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 48px; }

  .cond-hero { padding: 36px 0 28px; }
  .cond-tag {
    display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em;
    color: #0EA5E9; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding: 5px 12px; background: rgba(124,58,237,0.06); border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  }
  .cond-h1 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 34px);
    color: #111827; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .cond-h1 em { font-style: normal; color: #0EA5E9; }
  .cond-sub { font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 480px; }

  .cond-section { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .cond-h2 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800;
    color: #111827; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .cond-p { font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 14px; }

  /* ─── CARD GRID ─── */
  .cond-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
  .cond-card {
    padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 12px;
    background: #F8F9FB; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }
  .cond-card strong {
    display: block; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;
    color: #111827; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .cond-card p { font-size: 11px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ─── SIMPLE LIST ─── */
  .cond-list-simple {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
    padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 14px;
    background: #F8F9FB; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }
  .cond-list-simple div { font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.5; }
  .cond-list-simple strong { color: #111827; }

  /* ─── CALLOUTS ─── */
  .cond-callout { border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px 20px; }
  .cond-callout.women {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124,58,237,0.03), rgba(219,39,119,0.03));
    border: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.12);
  }
  .cond-callout.red { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.15); }
  .cond-callout.blue {
    background: rgba(96,165,250,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.15);
  }
  .cond-callout.blue p { font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0; }
  .cond-callout.blue strong { color: #111827; }
  .cond-cta {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 16px; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 50px;
    background: #0EA5E9; color: #fff; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s;
  }
  .cond-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(124,58,237,0.3); }

  .cond-check-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .cond-check-list div { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.5; }
  .cond-ck {
    width: 20px; height: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; border-radius: 5px;
    background: rgba(124,58,237,0.08); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #0EA5E9; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .cond-x {
    width: 20px; height: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; border-radius: 5px;
    background: rgba(248,113,113,0.08); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #f87171; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* ─── BUTTONS ─── */
  .cond-btns { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cond-btn {
    display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s;
  }
  .cond-btn.discord { background: #5865F2; color: #fff; }
  .cond-btn.discord:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(88,101,242,0.3); }
  .cond-btn.email { background: #F8F9FB; color: #6B7280; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
  .cond-btn.email:hover { border-color: #D1D5DB; color: #111827; }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .cond-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</Base>
